Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.81,0:22:27.06,Default,Default,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.06,0:22:33.27,Default,Default,0,0,0,,{\be2}저녁 노을 하늘 아래, 하루하루의 끝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.06,0:22:33.27,Default,Default,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.27,0:22:36.43,Default,Default,0,0,0,,{\be2}왠지 쓸쓸해졌는 걸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.27,0:22:36.43,Default,Default,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.43,0:22:38.18,Default,Default,0,0,0,,{\be2}하지만 즐거웠어, 잘 가!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.43,0:22:38.18,Default,Default,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.18,0:22:43.39,Default,Default,0,0,0,,{\be2}미소 지으며 손 흔들면 잘자, 내일 보자!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.18,0:22:43.39,Default,Default,0,0,0,,
