Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.39,0:22:49.85,Default,Default,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.85,0:22:56.47,Default,Default,0,0,0,,{\be2}Hurrah, Hurrah 뛰어들어 꼬마보이, \N아직 보지 못한 세계로
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.85,0:22:56.47,Default,Default,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.47,0:23:02.97,Default,Default,0,0,0,,{\be2}Let's Go, 날개짓 해 꼬마걸, 혼자가 아니야
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.47,0:23:02.97,Default,Default,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.97,0:23:09.52,Default,Default,0,0,0,,{\be2}실패해도 괜찮아 \N우리들은 막 시작했을 뿐이니까
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.97,0:23:09.52,Default,Default,0,0,0,,
